Title: Mac Guide
Message:
So you need to go to Finder -> Downloads -> Find CrunchLabsArduinoCreateAgent -> Open -> Drag the CreateAgent Icon into the Applications Folder -> Go back to Finder -> Applications -> CrunchlabsArduinoCreateAgent -> Open. The CreateAgent does not have a window that opens when you open it, it runs in the background. You can check to make sure it is running by looking at your system tray in the top right. If you see a black circle with the Hack Pack logo on it, then it is running. Also make sure to use chrome as Safari will not work unless you want to mess with your settings as described here https://discord.com/channels/1229106258749948056/1261395362963263488
