Title: Reflash Bootloader
Message:
Reflashing the bootloader can help nano's that don't allow uploading code due to "avrdude: stk500_recv()" errors, https://discord.com/channels/1229106258749948056/1304473086560829481/1304473086560829481
---
Title: IDE Errors Uploading Checklist
Message:
1. Use Chrome.
2. Use provided USB cable.
3. Connecting cable to silver USB-C on arduino, not black breadboard box.
4. Reload webpage.
5. Try in incognito mode
6. Turn off bluetooth + restart computer.
7. Try *multiple* other USB-A to USB-C cables.
8. Go to http://127.0.0.1:8991/ and send the "list" command
9. Worst case, try the Arduino IDE.
